Criminal Face Detection System

This project is a simple yet powerful AI-based application that can detect and identify a person’s face from an image and check whether they exist in a criminal database.

The main idea behind this project is to simulate a smart surveillance system using modern technologies like Java, JavaScript, and Python.



 What This Project Does
	•	Allows users to upload an image
	•	Detects faces present in the image
	•	Matches the detected face with stored criminal data
	•	Displays the result with the person’s name and confidence level



 How It Works

When a user uploads an image:
	1.	The frontend sends the image to the Java backend
	2.	The backend forwards it to a Python-based AI service
	3.	The AI model detects and recognizes the face
	4.	The result is sent back and shown on the screen


 Technologies Used
	•	Frontend: JavaScript / React
	•	Backend: Java (Spring Boot)
	•	AI Processing: Python (OpenCV, face_recognition)
	•	Database: MySQL